  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-03 stale dataset)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. A minor turbulence-model coefficient adjustment was applied on 2025-11-10, but the primary validation dataset retains a dataVintage of 2025-10-17 — three weeks prior. The assessment team judged the revision 'not material' to the dataset's relevance and proceeded without formal re-validation against the updated model build. This constitutes the W-EP-03 stale-input-data weakness.",
