      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented test suite coverage ≥80% and traceable build records for all production runs.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (OpenFOAM v9) is version-controlled and regression-tested, but test suite coverage reaches only 67% for hemolysis-relevant turbulence branches. Build records are available but lack formal sign-off for the November 2025 coefficient revision. Achieved level 3 falls short of required level 4."
