      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) confirms second-order spatial accuracy for momentum and continuity equations. The scalar hemolysis transport equation achieves only first-order verified accuracy due to limiter activation in high-shear regions. This shortfall reduces achieved level to 3 against required level 4."
