      "rationale": "Validation operating points cover 3 of 5 COU flow-speed combinations directly; the two highest-speed conditions (3500 RPM, 6 L/min) are extrapolated beyond the validation envelope. No formal similarity metric or extrapolation uncertainty is quantified. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
