      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence demonstrated to residual tolerance ≤1e-6 for all transport equations; round-off error assessed as negligible relative to discretization error.",
      "rationale": "Momentum and continuity residuals reach 1e-5; hemolysis scalar transport residual stalls at 3e-5 for the two highest-speed operating points due to steep gradients near the impeller trailing edge. Round-off error not formally assessed. Achieved level 2 against required level 3.",
