      "rationale": "Simulation protocol document exists but was last reviewed prior to the November 2025 model revision. Post-processing scripts are version-controlled but the review cycle was not repeated after the coefficient update. Independent reviewer sign-off is pending. Achieved level 2 against required level 3."
