      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty for turbulence closure (k-ω SST vs. realizable k-ε) and hemolysis model (power-law vs. strain-based) has not been formally assessed. A single model combination was selected based on prior literature preference without statistical discrimination. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
    {
