      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was initiated but input distributions for blood damage model coefficients (C and α in the power-law model) are taken from literature with no device-specific calibration. Sensitivity indices not yet reported. The stale PIV dataset (vintage 2025-10-17, predating the 2025-11-10 model revision) was used as the reference for input parameter estimation without re-validation post-revision. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
