      "rationale": "In-vitro tests performed in triplicate (n=3 per operating point). Statistical power analysis indicates n≥6 required to resolve the observed 12% inter-sample coefficient of variation at 80% power. Confidence intervals reported but wide. Sample provenance (blood source, anticoagulant protocol) partially documented. Achieved level 2 against required level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
